      <title>越南電動車製造商 VinFast 面臨的挑戰加劇了母公司 Vingroup 的風險</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vietnam-ev-maker-vinfasts-challenges-escalate-risk-parent-vingroup-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[隨著越南最大的企業集團 Vingroup 制定雄心勃勃的全球擴張計劃，加大電動車業務力度，該公司面臨虧損部門 VinFast Auto 帶來的日益嚴重的財務風險。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/vietnam-ev-maker-vinfasts-challenges-escalate-risk-parent-vingroup-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 00:05:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由於電力中斷影響資料中心運營，Applied Digital 季度虧損激增</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/applied-digital-misses-quarterly-revenue-estimate-amid-power-disruption-data-2024-04-11/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[資料中心營運商 Applied Digital 週四公佈季度虧損超出預期，原因是 1 月份停電阻礙了其一個設施的運營，導致該公司股價在盤後交易中下跌超過 8%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/applied-digital-misses-quarterly-revenue-estimate-amid-power-disruption-data-2024-04-11/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 20:25:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
